---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/986899742574624768
  Locus:
    Date: 19 Apr 2018
---
Not only is it the case that happy people are more willing to help others,
but as I generally point out, helping others is the best way to help
yourself, the best way to promote your own happiness. It is you, yourself,
who will receive the benefit.
